msgid "KSpaceDuel"
msgstr "Romduell"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kspaceduel.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Space Arcade Game"
msgstr "Arkade-romspel"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kspaceduel.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"In KSpaceDuel each of two possible players control a satellite spaceship "
"orbiting the sun. As the game progresses players have to eliminate the "
"opponent's spacecraft with bullets or mines."
msgstr ""
"I Romduell styrer to spelarar kvart sitt romskip i bane rundt sola. "
"Spelarane skal øydeleggje motstandaren sitt romskip med kuler eller miner."
